N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 2208.4 - Form and content of a PAR against an order of the district rent administrator

State Regulations
A person aggrieved by an order issued by the district
rent administrator may file a PAR against such order only on a form prescribed
by the administrator. Notes
